org.springframework.core.io.buffer

Class NettyDataBuffer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.core.io.buffer.NettyDataBuffer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataBuffer, PooledDataBuffer

    public class NettyDataBuffer
extends Object
implements PooledDataBuffer
    Implementation of the DataBuffer interface that wraps a Netty ByteBuf. Typically constructed with NettyDataBufferFactory.
    Since:
    5.0
    Author:
    Arjen Poutsma
